1) Sale of this mod or mods containing the code of the Syberia project is prohibited!
2) You are obliged to indicate the authors of the mod if you use the Syberia mod or parts of it in your projects/servers.
3) All modified versions of the Syberia mod must be publicly available on github and be forks of the original mod.
4) It is allowed to repack and modify the mod only with the indication of the authorship of the original mod present on the steam workshop page and in the game as watermark.
5) Monetization of dayz servers using this mod is allowed.
